{"tid":1259552,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請分享及支持  守．城-fortress-defenders","createTime":"2019-06-26T15:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T11:11:42.000Z","uid":244876,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"22d61c51a242d11f8357a72a8942b6b4975a562f","tid":1259552,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:11:05.000Z","msg":"本Facebook Page希望可以讓大家有更多新睇法，內容盡可能衝擊大家既思考角度<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E5%AE%88-%E5%9F%8E-Fortress-Defenders-671863216588540/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E5%25AE%2588-%25E5%259F%258E-Fortress-Defenders-671863216588540%2F&d=DodTvzQjJx20NomtZcTkrmZ69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=b7255cb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E5%AE%88-%E5%9F%8E-Fortress-Defenders-671863216588540/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有一班來自世界各地既香港人<br />\n佢地未必可以親自來到現場支持，聲援各位英雄好漢<br />\n但係都希望可以盡一分綿力<br />\n去宣傳，分享比更多人知<br />\n而家呢個香港政府係幾咁荒謬，無恥<br />\n上梁不正下梁歪<br />\n絕對係令大家非常失望<br />\n每一個人都會想守護自己的家，呢一場未必係最慘烈既杖，但係一定係最刻骨銘心既一場<br />\n過左今次大家未必再有機會凝聚到咁多人<br />\n但係<br />\n<br />\n我地相信公義必在我們身上，盡每一分每一力為香港，為下一代而奮鬥<br />\n<br />\nAn hour of wolves and shattered shields when the Age of Men<br />\ncomes crashing down. But it is not this day. This day we fight! By all that<br />\nyou hold dear on this good earth, I bid you stand, Men of the West!<br />\n魔戒 王者再臨  最後亞拉岡同眾中土同胞講<br />\n總有一日人類時代會被 一切邪惡所毀滅<br />\n但毀滅既日子唔會係今日發生，我地今日會勇力為一切而奮戰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">It was the best of times; It was the worst of times</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n守 &middot; 城 FORTRESS DEFENDERS&middot;2019年6月22日星期六<br />\n國學大師錢鍾書說，沒有夢，沒有感覺，人生最原始的睡，同時也是死的樣品。現在，城外的人想進去，城裡的人想出來。 <br />\n摧毀一座城市，不需要軍隊，不需要暴力。流言這東西，比流感蔓延的速度更快，比流星所蘊含的能量更巨大，比流氓更具有惡意，比流產更能讓人心力憔悴。 <br />\n守，養精蓄銳。攻，不敢造次。一攻一守，在於民心。 <br />\n無論立場如何，請你，與我們一起，守護，我城。<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nWe will recap in English ... later.<br />\nWe can&rsquo;t find the right words now."},{"pid":"e86d37d9ca7b2af842ce7aab4b571fa4563138be","tid":1259552,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:16:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9236e2e66cca3cd105bf041d48d7f0eb0c70ff69","tid":1259552,"uid":264040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:21:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aaee4b12eff10060ed27e475af0710709459de76","tid":1259552,"uid":264040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:22:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d1382415126aa4b05b90031c109ba1197b0b3aa","tid":1259552,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:38:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"86a78ae949bbd28f2720f846a636c19d85492807","tid":1259552,"uid":264040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563c25749ef76e2c8621cfeb560361b17160c5d8","tid":1259552,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:44:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a0b0124505bc3b8fbfaf3c3311556085c8f3a4c1","tid":1259552,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:53:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cd6bcc0c0c418e3c040bc12e930633842ce4b9a6","tid":1259552,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T15:57:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ba0bc5faae481645a84bb428f1e6a77794a38a0c","tid":1259552,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:03:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"661640e4f0ac7bfbbee11c5eec3e1e34ad4457b9","tid":1259552,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T16:21:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"39d8f4af5d341d63dfa44978cdb9109998e85606","tid":1259552,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,